import React from 'react'
import adminlogo from "../src/alogo@2x.png"
import "./MenuBase.css"
const MenuBase = ({

    children
}) => {
    return ( <
        div className = "back" >

        <
        nav className = "navbar navbar-light bg-white shadow-lg" >
        <
        a className = "navbar-brand"
        href = "#" >
        <
        img src = { adminlogo }
        width = "40"
        height = "40"
        alt = ""
        loading = "lazy" / >
        <
        /a> <
        /nav>


        { children }


        <
        /div>
    )
}
export default MenuBase;
